<!-- ── SKILLS ANATOMY ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="skills">
  <div class="layout-wrap">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-20">
      <div class="fi opacity-0 translate-y-[18px] transition-[opacity,transform] duration-[650ms] ease-out [&.in]:translate-y-0 [&.in]:opacity-100">
        <div class="mb-3.5 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-kicker before:text-[rgba(139,124,255,0.62)] before:content-['//_']">Content model</div>
        <h2 class="mb-5 font-display text-[clamp(30px,3.5vw,50px)] font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.06em]">Knowledge,<br>procedures<br><em class="not-italic text-accent">&amp; style.</em></h2>
        <p class="max-w-[520px] text-sm leading-[1.75] text-text-dim">
          Chain Hub organizes everything your AI needs to know into three simple categories. 
          Start with our <strong class="font-semibold text-text">pre-built templates</strong>, then 
          <strong class="font-semibold text-text">add your own knowledge</strong> so your AI works exactly how you want it to.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[13px] leading-[1.75] text-text-dim">
          <strong class="font-semibold text-text">Skills</strong> are specialized knowledge packs—like a "Brand Voice" guide or a "Legal Review" expert.
          <strong class="font-semibold text-text">Workflows</strong> are step-by-step procedures you can follow (often human-led checklists; the AI can help per step).
          <strong class="font-semibold text-text">Rules</strong> are the general guidelines for tone, formatting, and behavior that apply to every conversation.
          <strong class="font-semibold text-text">Agents</strong> live in <code class="text-[rgba(139,124,255,0.62)]">agents/*.md</code>—focused worker roles linked into supported editors.
          See <a href="#skills-agents-workflows" class="font-medium text-[rgba(139,124,255,0.62)] no-underline hover:underline">Skills, agents &amp; workflows</a> for who runs what.
          Together, they form a portable brain that grows with you.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fi grid grid-cols-1 gap-0.5 delay-100 opacity-0 translate-y-[18px] transition-[opacity,transform] duration-[650ms] ease-out [&.in]:translate-y-0 [&.in]:opacity-100">
        <div class="border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-[rgba(139,124,255,0.26)] md:p-7">
          <div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1.5">
            <div class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">◈</div>
            <div class="min-w-0 flex-1 text-[13px] font-medium text-text sm:flex-none">Skills</div>
            <div class="w-full text-[10px] text-accent sm:ml-auto sm:w-auto sm:text-right">Expert knowledge at your fingertips</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs leading-[1.65] text-text-dim">
            Add expert knowledge to your AI. From specific industry standards to your personal writing style, 
            skills tell your AI exactly what it needs to know to be your perfect assistant.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-[rgba(139,124,255,0.26)] md:p-7">
          <div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1.5">
            <div class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">⤳</div>
            <div class="min-w-0 flex-1 text-[13px] font-medium text-text sm:flex-none">Workflows</div>
            <div class="w-full text-[10px] text-accent sm:ml-auto sm:w-auto sm:text-right">Procedures &amp; checklists</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs leading-[1.65] text-text-dim">
            Step-by-step runbooks for you or your team—onboarding, audits, release gates—with optional AI help per step.
            Distinct from <code class="text-[rgba(139,124,255,0.62)]">.github/workflows/</code> CI files in a repo.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-[rgba(139,124,255,0.26)] md:p-7">
          <div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1.5">
            <div class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">⌥</div>
            <div class="min-w-0 flex-1 text-[13px] font-medium text-text sm:flex-none">Rules</div>
            <div class="w-full text-[10px] text-accent sm:ml-auto sm:w-auto sm:text-right">Set the standard</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs leading-[1.65] text-text-dim">
            Set the ground rules for your AI. Define the tone, language, and boundaries so every 
            interaction feels consistent and professional, no matter which AI tool you use.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
